overview: Backpackers Chanell Heart and Daisy Ducati get more than they bargained for when they end up at a spooky bed & breakfast. Real estate agent Ana Foxxx has had enough of her partner Lotus Lain, after the girl has lost them clients. Ana gives Lotus a piece of her mind... Studious Ivy Sherwood has a heart-to-heart with newly engaged pal Adriana Maya, after Adriana reveals plans to drop out of school. Finally Dr. Anya Ivy gives sage advice to pregnant patient Skyler Nicole...
title: Lesbian Beauties 15: All Black Beauties
